{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017JrshDMuB28HUi7aeB3kdD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's a summary of the findings:\n\n## Breaking API Change\n\nPR #1157 split the single metadata context key (`mdKey{}`) into two separate typed keys:\n- `mdIncomingKey{}` — set by the gRPC framework when a request arrives (server-side)\n- `mdOutgoingKey{}` — set by user code before making an RPC (client-side)\n\n`FromContext`/`NewContext` remain as deprecated wrappers in the new grpc-go, but the **etcd vendor copy has removed them entirely** — any old-API usage would be a compile error.\n\n## Affected etcd Files (non-vendor)\n\n**No compile errors** — etcd has already fully migrated to the new API.\n\n**Two critical runtime behavior regressions:**\n\n| File | Line | Issue | Severity |\n|------|------|-------|----------|\n| `proxy/grpcproxy/watch.go` | 104 | `FromOutgoingContext(stream.Context())` on server-side context | **Critical** |\n| `proxy/grpcproxy/lease.go` | 155 | `FromOutgoingContext(stream.Context())` on server-side context | **Critical** |\n\nAll other files (`util.go`, `interceptor.go`, `auth/store.go`, `clientv3/*`) use the correct API variant.\n\n## Critical: Metadata Forwarding\n\nBoth proxy files call `FromOutgoingContext` on server-side stream contexts. After the key split, server contexts hold metadata under `mdIncomingKey{}`, but `FromOutgoingContext` reads `mdOutgoingKey{}` — they never overlap. The call always returns `(nil, false)`, so:\n\n- `lostLeaderC` is **never initialized**\n- `MetadataRequireLeaderKey` is **silently ignored** for Watch and LeaseKeepAlive streams through the gRPC proxy\n- Clients requiring a leader via `MetadataRequireLeaderKey` lose that guarantee with no error\n\n**Fix**: Replace `FromOutgoingContext(stream.Context())` → `FromIncomingContext(stream.Context())` in both files.\n\nReports written to `/workspace/analysis/IMPACT_REPORT.md` and `/workspace/agent_output/answer.json`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2475,"cache_read_input_tokens":41734,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2475},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3cd2aa03-a444-4481-b8bf-46284d1bc1a8","uuid":"3aef7c51-9cf5-4190-bf26-f77e8bcbf837"}
